headline: Huntington Bank Wins 18 'Best Bank' Awards for Business, Middle Market Banking
summary: The Huntington National Bank has received 18 "Best Bank" awards as part of the 2025 Coalition Greenwich Awards for the banking, financing and investing services it delivered last year to small businesses and middle market companies across the U.S.
